You are at a Cliff Base.

Here, the hard, dry desert floor scatters away from the cliff.

There is a pile of discarded bones here.

The ground to the northeast slopes slightly downhill and you hear a faint rustling sound coming from that direction.  To the east is an expanse of flat ground.  You can also climb up the path that heads north.

> east

> east

You are in a Sprawling Desert.

There is a lot of sand here, some of it forming some sand dunes.

You hear some voices, but no matter how hard you try, you cannot tell what direction they are coming from.

Back to the west you see a cliff rising up from the horizon.  If you look toward the south, you see a few small mounds peaking up from the desert floor.  A sandy, blown over path appears to continue to the east.  The desert appears to expand endlessly in all other directions.

> hide

> hide

The voice fades until you can no longer hear the speaker.

You are hiding behind the sand dune.

You have hidden yourself behind the sand dune in the sprawling desert.  You cannot go anywhere except back into the sprawling desert.  You sense that there is someone walking around just on the other side of the sand dune.

There is a swarm of really obnoxious bugs flying around back here.

To return to the sprawling desert, you'll need to 'unhide' or 'emerge'.

