> turn on machine

> turn on machine
You flip the lever upward so it is pointing to the on position.  It produces a soft hum and a small purple light shows at the base of the machine.
The machine begins to hum a little louder... The hair on your arms tingle.
The machine begins to hum louder.  The hair on your neck and arms is now standing at attention.
The low pitched hum from the machine is so loud now that the floor begins to vibrate and your heart feels like it is fluttering.
The hum of the machine reaches a crescendo and you hear a loud crack like the snapping of a whip and a faint purple light illuminates the lid of the machine.  The machine falls silent.
> open machine

> open machine
You have opened the machine.  In the machine, you see a plate.
