You are in a Town Square.

This area looks like it fell right out of an old western movie.  There are exits to the run-down, small buildings in ever direction except to the north and northwest.  Above each of the buildings are wooden signs that are painted with the name of the building.

You also notice a large speaker atop the eastern most building.

There is also a tall cylindrical scaffolding attached to the building to the southeast.

> southeast

> southeast

You are in a Doctors Office.

You have walked into a room filled with odd looking scientific equipment.  You're under the assumption that this used to be a doctor's office.  There are various, unimportant, and dusty books on a bookshelf that you can tell are medical tomes.  Of all the odd equipment in here, the only thing that really catches your eye is an odd looking machine that is resting on the patient table.

The doorway to the northwest has a strange yellow-purple hue to it, as if it were charged with energy.  There is a sign above a small door to the south that reads 'Laboratory'.

