From the north, you hear a loud voice.  "Report immediately to the Sheriff's Office.  Repeat:  All available units, report immediately to the Sheriff's Office."
> north

> north

You are in a Jail.

You are in a very small room.  In the southwest corner of this room is a small cell.  The door is standing ajar and it looks like you could easily go into the cell.

> break window with shovel

> break window with shovel
You chuck the shovel at the window like a javelin.  The shovel point hits in the center, javelins through it like butter and disappears into the town square.  The window is obliterated as tiny fragments of glass fly everywhere.

You peak through the opening of the wall and see the man dressed in black strutting over to the jail room.  He looks motivated and angry.  Perhaps you should make a run for it?
> in

> in

You are in a prison cell.

This room is dark and drab.  There is a slab of wood securely fastened to the floor here that you could only imagine was once a bed for whatever prisoner was the guest.  The slots in the iron bars are just large enough for you to fit your skinny arms through but that's about it.

There is a door leading back out into the jail room.

The commotion you made has certainly attracted the attention of Dingo's henchmen outside.  He is bound to find you soon.
You've dawdled long enough.  One, or both,  of those madmen are closing in on your location.  I hope you have a plan!  If so, get on with it!
You cower when the rocket launching lunatic bursts into the room.
He spots you cowering in the cell and readies his rocket launcher.  You have the nerve to look into his eyes (while praying this ridiculous plan of yours works) and you see a flash of what you might describe as pure evil flicker in his eyes.

He slings the rocket launcher onto his back and he struts calmly over to the prison cell.  He cackles evilly and speaks to you in a raspy whisper, "You starve now.  Rat."

He grabs a hold of the cell door to slam it shut and he instantly begins to shake violently.  The groans and grunts and gurgles that escape his convulsing body almost make you wish you hadn't done it this way.  Just as you are about to throw up from the sight of all of this, the man in black collapses to the floor.

His smoking body gives off a foul and unpleasant odor, which doesn't help your nausea.  At least he's no longer suffering.
> search corpse

> search corpse
You hesitate to reach out and touch the dead man, but considering the circumstances, you go through with it.

With fore finger and thumb, you open the breast of his robe and see a single key tucked in a small pocket.
> take gold key

> take gold key
You pick it up.
You snatch the key quickly and carefully away from the pocket of the dead man.
