You are in a Northeastern Patrol Area.

You are in a large rocky field.  There is a faint footworn path that heads off to the west.  At the end of the path you see a man dressed in a black robe.  Currently, he is staring westward down the length of an enormous stone wall.

There is an ominous warning sign bolted to a post in the ground just to the right of the guard's station.

There are exits to the west along the path and to the southeast. There is currently a patrol guard here who is looking away from you at the moment put continues to scan the area along the wall in front of him for possible intruders.  He is blocking the path westward.

> use pod launcher on warning sign

> use pod launcher on warning sign
You bring the pod launcher to your lips, aim at the giant sign, and blow with all your might.  The pod whistles out of the launcher and plunks hard against the sign.  As it does, it erupts into a small white cloud of smoke.

The guard spins around and sees you.  His eyes are burning with rage.  He draws his pistols and takes a step toward you.  He raises his pistols...

and yawns.

He drops his guns to the ground and looks at you confused.  The guard yawns again and collapses to the ground.  Soon he begins to snore.  As you muster the courage to approach him, he mysteriously disappears right before your eyes.  The path to the west is now open.
