Time passes.
> wait

> wait
Time passes.

You begin to do that but are stopped immediately when a searing pain creeps across the back of your skull.  You crumble forward and collapse onto the ground.  You look up trying to see who it was who clobbered you from behind.

All you see is the butt of a rifle rushing down toward your face.

"STOP!"

The butt of the gun stops mere inches from your face.

"Yes sir, Dr. Dingo," replies the man with the gun.

Your vision is blurry and you feel yourself fading into unconsciousness.  Your vision blurs and you try to focus, glancing back in the direction of 'Dr. Dingo'...

Before you black out, you lock eyes and see your old, trusted friend, Marcus Straussberger wearing a white Dingo robe and a devilish grin.

